Class Identifier

java.lang.Object
  project3.three.Node
      project3.lex.Token
          project3.lex.Argument
              project3.lex.Identifier

public class Identifier
extends Argument

An Identifier token. This is not needed for assignment 1, but is included in the lex package to make it easier to read the code in project 3.

Syntax: Letter [Letter | Digit ]* 

 Domain Definition:
     type       : TokenType -- inherited from Token
     value      : String    -- inherited from Token
     lineNumber : int       -- inherited from Token

 Instance Invariant:
